com.terei.jvector.util
Class DynamicIntArray

java.lang.Object
  com.terei.jvector.util.DynamicIntArray

public class DynamicIntArray
extends Object

This class stores an array of ints, but provides dynamic functions to add, and remove values from the array. The array can also grow as nesseccary.
